      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/02/22/us/politics/iran-terrorist-attacks-proxies-trump.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着特朗普总统考虑对伊朗发动另一场军事行动，安全官员正在监测越来越令人担忧的迹象。]]></description>
